            <section class="lg:col-span-2 bg-white shadow-lg rounded-xl p-6">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-4 pb-2 border-b-2 border-blue-200">About Me</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                    Hello! I'm Kartik Jaswal, a passionate and tech-savvy individual with a keen interest in software development, data analysis, and emerging technologies. I thrive on solving complex problems and am always eager to learn new tools and methodologies to enhance my skills.
                </p>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                    My journey in technology is driven by curiosity and a desire to build impactful solutions. I am committed to continuous learning and staying abreast of the latest advancements in the tech world.
                </p>
            </section>

            <!-- Skills Section -->
